托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/tony-hawk-responds-to-rumours-to-rumours-of-a-new-pro-skater-game-game-game-3840736?utm_source = rsss＆utm_medium_medium = rsss＆utm_campaightony-hawkk---campaign = tony-hawkk--响应新的及新派 - 斯基特游戏Ali ShutlerMon, 24 Feb 2025 11:38:13 +0000 Gaming NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3840736 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="&#39;托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）的Pro Skater 1+2&#39;。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一个神秘的倒计时指向3月初的揭露</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/tony-hawk-responds-to-rumours-of-a-new-pro-skater-game-3840736">托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）的帖子回应了关于新的“ Pro Swerter”游戏的谣言，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="&#39;托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）的Pro Skater 1+2&#39;。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tony-Hawks-Pro-Skater-12-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）回应了许多谣言，即未来几周将在未来几周内揭幕一场新的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/tony-hawks-pro-skater"><em>溜冰者</em></a>比赛。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/like-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii-review-sega-3839486">“像龙：夏威夷海盗雅库扎”评论：日本犯罪传奇袭击了海洋</a></li></ul><p><em>托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）的职业滑冰运动员</em>于1999年首次发行，并催生了许多续集和衍生产品，尽管最后一场主线游戏于2015年发行。修复的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/tony-hawks-pro-skater-1-and-2">托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）的托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）的Pro Skater 1+2</a></em>在2021年出现，但计划在第三次刷新的计划中当<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/vicarious-visions-is-no-more-as-it-officially-becomes-part-of-blizzard-entertainment-3204022">Activision Blizzard收购了开发人员替代视觉时，该系列中的第四场比赛被废弃了。</a></p><p> 2024年，托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）暗示，“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/tony-hawk-gives-update-on-new-pro-skater-game-3793467">球迷将真正欣赏</a>”的一款新<em>职业滑冰</em>运动员正在进行中，本月早些时候，专业滑冰运动员Tyshawn Jones透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/new-tony-hawks-pro-skater-remaster-game-release-date-3839358">他参与了一场新的托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）的比赛</a>。上周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-teasing-new-tony-hawks-pro-skater-3840116"><em>《使命召唤》</em>球迷在<em>托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）的专业滑冰</em>徽标下发现了一个约会，这是<em>黑色行动6</em>的磨损水平</a>。几个小时后，<a href="https://www.tonyhawkthegame.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）官方的滑冰运动员</em>网站</a>上也出现了类似的倒计时。</p><p>现在，滑板传奇回应了谣言，即格林尼治标准时间将于3月4日下午6:30宣布一场新游戏。</p><p> “在Black Ops 6的Grind MP Map中发现了与<em>Tony Hawk的Pro Skater</em>相关的预告片！ <em>3</em><a href="https://x.com/Xbox/status/1892643631141388678" target="_blank" rel="noopener">月</a>4<a href="https://x.com/tonyhawk/status/1892622967579832757" target="_blank" rel="noopener">日</a><a href="https://x.com/charlieINTEL/status/1892621320598208577" target="_blank" rel="noopener">的</a>宣布。 </p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="qme" dir="ltr"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f440.png" alt="👀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p> - 托尼·霍克（@tonyhawk） <a href="https://twitter.com/tonyhawk/status/1892622967579832757?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年2月20日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>一位粉丝<a href="https://x.com/atomx626/status/1892959306858791215" target="_blank" rel="noopener">写道</a>：“请托尼先生先生，<em>美国荒原的</em>重新制作。” “从来没有打过<em>托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）的Pro Skater 3和4</em> ，所以您不知道如果他们重塑这两场比赛，我会感到多么兴奋，”另一人<a href="https://x.com/METALGOD2K/status/1892676212893376711" target="_blank" rel="noopener">说</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/tony-hawk-celebrates-25th-anniversary-of-pro-skater-promises-series-has-a-future-3798182">霍克（Hawk）回顾了<em>托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）去年托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）的职业滑冰运动员</em>的遗产</a>，他写道：我对比赛的意图和期望主要是为了享受滑板运动员的乐趣。我不知道它会超越一个利基市场，以取得巨大的成功，并且正如某些人所说的那样，改变了滑板的流行过程（甚至可能是滑板技巧的演变）。这肯定改变了我的一生，这是我今天乘坐滑板的重要原因。而且，大多数特色角色仍在撕裂并以最佳方式代表滑板的多样性。”</p><p>在其他新闻中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/game-of-thrones">《权力的游戏》</a></em>作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-r-r-martin">乔治·RR·马丁（George RR Martin）</a>确认有关于<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/elden-ring">埃尔登戒指</a></em>电影的“一些谈话”  - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/george-r-r-martin-elden-ring-movie-game-of-thrones-delay-3840707">但他可能没有参与其中，</a>因为他仍然有一本书要完成。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/tony-hawk-responds-to-rumours-of-a-new-pro-skater-game-3840736">托尼·霍克（Tony Hawk）的帖子回应了关于新的“ Pro Swerter”游戏的谣言，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
